    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices that consist of a heavyweight hinge with an added pivot using the same pin. The leaves of the pivot interlock with the hinge leaves. Two conventional hinges are required to complete the set.</Note_Text>
